<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ginhawa | Predict. Prevent. Perform.</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900">
    <nav class="p-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">Ginhawa</div>
        <div>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/logout" class="ml-4 text-gray-600">Logout</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/login" class="text-gray-600 mr-4">Login</a>
                <a href="/signup" class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg">Get Started</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="py-20 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">Predict. Prevent. Perform.</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Empowering students and educators to detect burnout risk before it hits. Using AI-driven insights to keep you at your peak performance.</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="/signup" class="px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-700 transition">Get Started – It’s Free</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-center">
            <div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl">1</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Connect Data</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Sync with your LMS or log your daily sleep, study, and stress levels manually.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl">2</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">AI Analysis</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Our engine identifies patterns in your grades, sleep, and habits to calculate burnout risk.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl">3</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Personalized Action</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Receive custom recommendations, wellness tips, and resource links to stay healthy.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Trusted by Students & Educators</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 px-6">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border italic text-gray-700">
                    "This tool helped me realize my sleep habits were the main reason for my dropping grades. It's a lifesaver!" - Sarah, Student
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border italic text-gray-700">
                    "An invaluable resource for early intervention. I can now support students before they reach a crisis point." - Mr. Thompson, Counselor
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">FERPA Compliant</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">COPPA Compliant</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-12 bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 text-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 mb-4">
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white">About</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white">Privacy</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white">Contact</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white">For Schools</a>
        </div>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Ginhawa. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
